definitions.explanation_en: A proper noun used as a given name, typically masculine, of modern origin and popular in English-speaking countries. It may be a variant of 'Jason' or an independent creation.
definitions.explanation_cn: 用作人名的专有名词，通常为男性名，起源于现代，在英语国家中较为流行。它可能是 'Jason' 的变体，也可能是独立创造的名字。
definitions.example_en: Jace is the captain of the school's debate team.
definitions.example_cn: 杰斯是学校辩论队的队长。
